    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Describe your family.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 30 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Hello, I'm {name}. I have a big family: I have two parents, six sisters any brother but I have three brothers-in-law and one niece. My niece, her mother and the sister's husband live in Italy. I have also twenty-nine cousins and fourten uncle and tant</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment">Good family labels but no more than that.</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment">A1 or A2; A1 errors but A2 phrases. More text is needed.</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
        </body>
